msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/Fred-Foobar.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`J--Random-Hacker`\\'s cousin. Any typical human being, more or less "
"synonymous with ‘someone’ except that Fred Foobar can be "
":ref:`backreference`\\d by name later on. \"So Fred Foobar will enter his "
"phone number into the database, and it'll be archived with the others. "
"Months later, when Fred searches...\" See also :ref:`Bloggs-Family` and "
":ref:`Dr--Fred-Mbogo`"
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`J--Random-Hacker`\\ のいとこ。任意のごく一般的な人間で、‘someone(誰か)’とほぼ同義だが、Fred "
"Foobarは後で名前によって\\ :ref:`backreference`\\ できる点が異なる。「それでFred "
"Foobarが自分の電話番号をデータベースに入力すると、それは他のものと一緒にアーカイブされる。何ヶ月か後、Fredが検索すると……」。\\ "
":ref:`Bloggs-Family`\\ と\\ :ref:`Dr--Fred-Mbogo`\\ も参照。"
